values: helloo, this entry will be half update/ half vent. well, you know when you have a lot of time to yourself i.e being sick at home all week or being home on a yucky saturday . .you just think about things. and i hate thinking about things and since you have nothing to do, you exaggerate things and you have a lot of what if's. people in relationships will probably understand this more than those who aren't, but stay with me here. i'll start thinking about these things and i jump to conclusions, or i'll just create different scenarios in my head that could have gone on, are going on, or will happen. and it drives me crazy! and then i get really fucking pissed off, like how dare he let me think these things! but, it's not his fault entirely. obviously, i have reason enough to begin with to think about them as much as i do but the jumping to conclusions and having bad dreams about them are all on me. but then i think, is it a sign? or is it like intuition.. or am i just being a dumb insecure 16 year old girl. for the most part, i go with the 2nd. but, it still leaves some things unanswered. i'm not trying to be philisophical here, it's just i feel like things are being kept from me, maybe for my own good actually. most people reading this are like wtf is this crazy bitch talking about? well, to tell the truth i don't know either. i just need to write some of these feelings down, so maybe i can better understand them. i think these feelings or thoughts just come automatically with having a long term relationship [year & 5 months to be exact.] and i wonder if he has these thoughts but then i realize he's a guy and they don't think about that too much. and i don't want to give the impression that i'm in a secretive, horrible relationship because i'm not at all. he does things that make me believe that i really am the only one for him. but then, i watch movies and TV and read books where people have 2 sides to them. and that really makes me sad. i don't want to be one of those people who finds out something about their boyfriend/girlfriend that totally blows them away and leaves them feeling cheated or dooped or regretting their relationship. and mine is nowhere near that point. once again, these are all what if's . . and i feel like i've been preparing myself somewhat to hear these things and maybe that's why i dream so much. does anyone feel me on this? :/ like the last thing i want to do is portray my boyfriend as an asshole because he does a lot of great things for me, just there is a lot of what if's. well, last night i went out to dinner at fridays with justina, danielle & jon. <3fridays, yess<3 danielllee justinaaa hahahaha

what up . . why do i suck at updating this thing, don't know. so randomly at 3 am monday morning, my throat starts KILLING me. so i stayed home, went to the doctor's, found out i have the flu [and yes i was one of those people who didn't give a fuck about the shortage of the flu vaccine] so that suckkked but i did get to stay home tuesday & wednesday too. mikey came over wednesday because i was going through some stuff, <3. i went to school on thursday because it was a shortened day, wasn't too bad. we changed volleyball teams, yeaa mine's awesome with colleen & petruzzi :D. we changed seats in physics too, that shit sucks. i miss lucas and krista :(. whatevs, now i got me some luisa & macnamara. i woke up yesterday and got ready for school but then felt like SUCH shit, i ended up staying home too. i want to say thankkk you for everyone who left me messages online, texts, voicemails etc etc to see how i was, i lovee you. happy 18th birthday to sean hogan! last night, i felt better so i went out to dinner with jeff, bobby, and mike. fridays had a mad long wait so we ended up going to walmart & fucking aroumd, hah. fridays was still beat so we ended up going to the diner, but i don't eat diner food so that sucked,but i got a salad from mcdonalds on the way home, so i guess it was okay. not anything like a fridays salad, right danielle? <3myfridaysslutt. mike came back here with me & twister was on! today, i'm sleeping all day so i can go outt tonight, yay. a boogs. <33. yep, right up my noseeee. your lips, they pout & twist. oooh i'm so emo with my side bangs. blue eyes. hiding in my bed. i must've thought this face was cool or something bc im doing it in every pic.

love it. bling bling, money ain't a thing. boogs in action. sephora bags galore :D. <3 arden b <3 bebe 4eva. urban decaaaaaaaay! so cute. adorable.

ugh. i went over danielle's on monday afterschool and we talked about our futures & everything. it just made me really want to get out of morris hills!! i chilled w/ greg & telep the other night, we drove around looking for christmas lights :) and ofcourse shopped! a black coach wristlet which is SO cute! the urbay decay xxx lipslick set, anddd the lovespell giftset from victoria secret! it was sooooo nice of her :). we went over mike's aunt's house and i met a lot of his family, it was nice :). we left after a couple hours & drove around . . went over his grandma's, looked at baby pictures of mike & his brothers, awee! we left & walked to church and did the whole midnight mass thing together, the priest was drunk i think. he was talking about trolls & folger cans, yea i know. christmas was AMAZING!! i opened awesome presents and then my mom told me i had missed some things on the tree, sooo i look up and see all of these gold sephora bags! fillled with urban decay make up, perfume, and soo much stuff. it was awesome :). jason & kyle came over later and we gave kyle his finding nemo activity scooter thing, he was soooo cute! :). watched so many christmas home movies & ate lots all day, then mikey came over. i gave him his many presents & he gave me mine. omg, he gave me the tiffany floating heart necklace, i screamed literally haha. thanks boogs! we watched a little of 'it's a wonderful life' & went to the movies to see lemony snicket's a series of unfortunate events, seriously it was sooooooo good! not at all what i expected :). today, i put my christmas money to use and went shopping with mommy, got a lot of stuff. i've been sleeping ALL DAY! i was exhausted from this last month of chaos. nowwww, i'm going to take a bubble bath & watch spiderman2 with the fam. <33 merry xmas everyone, ill post pics.

so sam & i are going to see madison somehow in franklinville next weekend.

should be fuuuunn. ;)

Ugh, like fuck that shit. i just think way too fucking much, my brain needs to stop. i hung out with mike again afterschool today and he made me watch lord of the rings. i fell asleep. the oc premieres on thursday, hotness. 4 day weekend coming up, hell yea. i hope john kerry wins. i wish i could vote.
